line_1: Vast crowds of Pimps and Noseless Whores,
By this distinction all your whores
line_2: And courtiers I turn out of doors,

line_1: Make Scots speak Treason, cozen subtlest Whores,
line_2: A Tongue that can cheat Widows, cancel Scores,

line_1: Was ever known such Sons of Whores?
Whoremasters peers, and sons of whores;
